{"tid":1593350,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"只推主線PO！！！！","createTime":"2019-09-25T04:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T04:44:44.000Z","uid":300006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6c4cab10c6316e18c3f46487dbc78b35de8519e7","tid":1593350,"uid":300006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:37:39.000Z","msg":"只推主線PO，結集行動優先重要<br />\n分線PO唔好濫開令主線沉，先做記錄，綜合討論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家唔好再做偵探</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n戰爭會有死傷，大家心情都一樣好沉重<br />\n但無人會忘記義士受到既不公對待<br />\n無人會唔憤怒<br />\n我地無一個人想失去手足，然後再失去勝利<br />\n<br />\n大家要團結，連同犧牲既義士既付出去抗爭<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權先對得住犧牲既義士</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係P牌，為P牌既無能慨嘆"},{"pid":"eae740501f44e6235f0137a93dd45e3a6c284f7a","tid":1593350,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"2c899ba3c102eae840726db1e8a2c8a6554b955c","tid":1593350,"uid":300006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:38:25.000Z","msg":"搵人幫手推下唔該！"},{"pid":"1577abc16bccbb34ae762c700e6e98c923d5998f","tid":1593350,"uid":261530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:38:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06382327d1a4423d9d94310ef918fbf140caa1fb","tid":1593350,"uid":300006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:38:35.000Z","msg":"搵人幫手推下唔該！"},{"pid":"8c96232639dbba704500f0aa649ede573ccbb990","tid":1593350,"uid":300006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:38:47.000Z","msg":"搵人幫手推下唔該！"},{"pid